  "timeline-content/1888.html": "<div class=\"accordion-nested-container\">\n                    <details class=\"accordion-custom accordion-nested\">\n                        <summary>\n                            <div class=\"summary-inner\">\n                                <span class=\"icon-circle-svg icon-sky\">\n                                    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M20 2H4c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v18l4-4h14c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V4c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2z\"/></svg>\n                                </span>\n                                <h4>Annual Catalogue</h4>\n                            </div>\n                            <span class=\"chevron\"></span>\n                        </summary>\n                        <div class=\"details-content\">\n                            <div class=\"context-card context-card-sky\">\n                                <p>The school's official catalogue documents the curriculum, faculty, and admission requirements of the era. Scroll through the full document below:</p>\n                                <div style=\"width:100%; height:460px; border-radius:6px; overflow:hidden; border: 1px solid var(--color-accent-sage); margin-top: 10px;\">\n                                    <iframe src=\"../assets/annual_catalogue.pdf\" width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" style=\"border:none; display:block;\" title=\"Annual Catalogue PDF\"></iframe>\n                                </div>\n                                <a href=\"../assets/annual_catalogue.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"display:inline-block; margin-top:10px; font-size:0.85rem; color:var(--color-accent-sage);\">&#8599; Open full PDF in new tab</a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </details>\n                </div>",
  "timeline-content/1900.html": "<div class=\"accordion-nested-container\">\n                    <details class=\"accordion-custom accordion-nested\">\n                        <summary>\n                            <div class=\"summary-inner\">\n                                <span class=\"icon-circle-svg icon-sky\">\n                                    <svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path d=\"M16 11c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S17.66 5 16 5c-1.66 0-3 1.34-3 3s1.34 3 3 3zm-8 0c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S9.66 5 8 5 5 6.34 5 8s1.34 3 3 3zm0 2c-2.33 0-7 1.17-7 3.5V19h14v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5zm8 0c-.29 0-.62.02-.97.05 1.16.84 1.97 1.97 1.97 3.45V19h6v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5z\"/></svg>\n                                </span>\n                                <h4>The 1899 Class Photos</h4>\n                            </div>\n                            <span class=\"chevron\"></span>\n                        </summary>\n                        <div class=\"details-content\">\n                            <div class=\"context-card context-card-sky\">\n                                <p>These photographs from 1899 capture three distinct tracks of study at Roger Williams University, representing the graduating year before the Paris Exposition.</p>\n\n                                <div class=\"inner-card border-left-sage mb-12 padding-16\">\n                                    <h5><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" fill=\"var(--color-accent-sage)\"><path d=\"M16 11c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S17.66 5 16 5c-1.66 0-3 1.34-3 3s1.34 3 3 3zm-8 0c1.66 0 2.99-1.34 2.99-3S9.66 5 8 5 5 6.34 5 8s1.34 3 3 3zm0 2c-2.33 0-7 1.17-7 3.5V19h14v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5zm8 0c-.29 0-.62.02-.97.05 1.16.84 1.97 1.97 1.97 3.45V19h6v-2.5c0-2.33-4.67-3.5-7-3.5z\"/></svg> Normal Class (1899)</h5>\n                                    <img src=\"../assets/1899_normal_class.jpg\" alt=\"1899 Normal Class\" class=\"thumbnail-img-inline\">\n                                    <p class=\"font-size-90\">Students training to become teachers &mdash; the backbone of Black education across the South.</p>\n                                    <div class=\"cb\"></div>\n                                </div>\n\n                                <div class=\"inner-card border-left-sage mb-12 padding-16\">\n                                    <h5><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" fill=\"var(--color-accent-sage)\"><path d=\"M12 3L1 9l4 2.18v6L12 21l7-3.82v-6l2-1.09V17h2V9L12 3zm6.82 6L12 12.72 5.18 9 12 5.28 18.82 9zM17 15.99l-5 2.73-5-2.73v-3.72l5 2.73 5-2.73v3.72z\"/></svg> Academic Class (1899)</h5>\n                                    <img src=\"../assets/1899_academic_class.jpg\" alt=\"1899 Academic Class\" class=\"thumbnail-img-inline\">\n                                    <p class=\"font-size-90\">The collegiate track offering rigorous academic coursework to prepare graduates for leadership roles.</p>\n                                    <div class=\"cb\"></div>\n                                </div>\n\n                                <div class=\"inner-card border-left-sage padding-16\">\n                                    <h5><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" width=\"18\" height=\"18\" fill=\"var(--color-accent-sage)\"><path d=\"M12 3L1 9l4 2.18v6L12 21l7-3.82v-6l2-1.09V17h2V9L12 3zm6.82 6L12 12.72 5.18 9 12 5.28 18.82 9zM17 15.99l-5 2.73-5-2.73v-3.72l5 2.73 5-2.73v3.72z\"/></svg> Ministers Class (1899)</h5>\n                                    <img src=\"../assets/1899_ministers_class.jpg\" alt=\"1899 Ministers Class\" class=\"thumbnail-img-inline\">\n                                    <p class=\"font-size-90\">Theological training for Black ministers to serve growing communities across the South.</p>\n                                    <div class=\"cb\"></div>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </details>\n                </div>",
